[[Spear Phishing]] is a kind of [[Phishing|Phishing Attack]], widespread in the social networks.

It tries to induce the victim to do something stupid (like give away the money or the number of the credit card) by pretending to have a personal relationship like a mutual friend, or claiming to work for the same company.